00:00:00,160 --> 00:00:03,919
Sam Altman predicted AI would
create the first one person

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:07,589
billion dollar company. It just
happened and it's not what

3
00:00:07,639 --> 00:00:12,429
you think. Matthew Gallagher built
a telehealth company called Medvi

4
00:00:12,480 --> 00:00:16,309
from his living room in
LA. He sells GLP1 weight

5
00:00:16,359 --> 00:00:21,600
loss drugs online. He outsources
the doctors, the prescriptions and

6
00:00:21,679 --> 00:00:25,539
the shipping. His only full
time hire. His brother He

7
00:00:25,609 --> 00:00:29,769
he spent $20,000 and two
months building the whole thing.

8
00:00:29,850 --> 00:00:33,759
ChatGPT and Claude wrote his
code midjourney and Runway made

9
00:00:33,810 --> 00:00:37,960
his ads. 11 labs and
custom AI agents handle customer

10
00:00:38,009 --> 00:00:43,359
service. First year revenue $401
million. This year Medvai is

11
00:00:43,409 --> 00:00:48,439
on pace for 1.8 billion.
No massive team, no venture

12
00:00:48,490 --> 00:00:53,509
backed army of engineers. Just
one founder and AI doing

13
00:00:53,560 --> 00:00:57,109
the work of hundreds. Altman
said this would have been

